Document: VisualShaderNodeBillboard
Path: godot/classes/class_visualshadernodebillboard.rst
Summary: Describes the VisualShaderNodeBillboard class and its required connection to the Model View Matrix output port.

The output port of this node needs to be connected to Model View Matrix port of VisualShaderNodeOutput. This node is used to control billboard behavior in visual shaders, ensuring geometry faces the camera. The connection to the Model View Matrix port is mandatory for proper shader functionality.
