Path: godot/classes/class_visualshadernodebillboard.rst
Summary: Properties for controlling billboard behavior in visual shaders, including type and scaling options.

- billboard_type (Enum): Type of billboard. Default: 1 (BillboardType)
- keep_scale (bool): Whether to maintain original scale when applying billboard transformations. Default: false

Note: BillboardType enum values map to specific rendering behaviors (e.g., 1 represents standard billboard type).
